    "title": "Manufacturing Engineer - Adani Enterprises Advisory Limited - Experienced Professionals",
    "description": "Adani Enterprises Advisory Limited invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Manufacturing Engineer at our Srinagar location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Adani Enterprises Advisory Limited:\nAdani Enterprises Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Adani Enterprises Advisory Limited!",
